 little embarrassing to name a boat for the federal rule of criminal proced=
ure that kept you out of prison. Getting acquitted on a Rule 29 motion is n=
ot at all =E2=80=9Ca technicality,=E2=80=9D it is the opposite of a technic=
ality, it is a judge finding that you are innocent and the government=E2=80=
=99s case is ridiculous, but still, the name does rather draw attention to =
that time you were charged with a crime. But mostly=C2=A0I think it's great=
. =E2=80=9CBehind every great fortune <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
