=E2=80=9D is I suppose a reasonable theory to have at the marina. =E2=80=9C=
I=E2=80=99m on a boat and not in prison due to Rule 29,=E2=80=9D you can te=
ll your neighbor at the dock; =E2=80=9Cwhat about you?=E2=80=9D</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway that article is in part about Bogucki=E2=80=99s=
